    "title": "Tohara katika Agano Jipya",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "tohara katika agano jipya",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Tohara, ambayo ni kuondoa govi la mwanaume, ilikuwa ya kawaida katika Mashariki ya Karibu ya kale (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:25-Jer9:26\">Yeremia 9:25–26</a>). Kwa Wayahudi, ilikuwa na umuhimu wa kidini kama ishara ya agano (makubaliano maalum) ambayo Mungu alifanya na watu wa Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:9-Gen17:14\">Mwanzo 17:9–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:2\">Yoshua 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:22\">Yohana 7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:8\">Matendo 7:8</a>; Siraki 44:20). Kawaida walifanya hivyo siku ya nane baada ya kuzaliwa kwa mtoto wa kiume (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:12\">Mwanzo 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:3\">Mambo ya Walawi 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:59\">Luka 1:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:8\">Matendo 7:8</a>).</p><p>Agano Jipya linataja tohara ya Yohana Mbatizaji, Yesu, na mitume Paulo na Timotheo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:59\">Luka 1:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:21\">2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:2-Acts16:3\">Matendo 16:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:5\">Wafilipi 3:5</a>). Tohara pia ikawa ishara ya upyaisho wa uhusiano wa mtu na Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:16\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:6\">30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:4\">Yeremia 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:28-Rom2:29\">Warumi 2:28–29</a>). Mwishoni mwa miaka ya 40 Baada ya Kristo (BK), baadhi ya Wakristo wa Kiyahudi walitaka Wakristo wa Mataifa (wasio Wayahudi) wafanyiwe tohara (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:1\">Matendo 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:5\">5</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:20-Acts21:21\">21:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:4\">Wagalatia 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11-Gal2:13\">11–13</a>). Hata hivyo, Paulo na Barnaba hawakukubaliana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:2\">Matendo 15:2</a>). Baraza la kanisa huko Yerusalemu liliamua kwamba watu wa Mataifa hawahitaji kufanyiwa tohara (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:19-Acts15:21\">15:19–21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28-Acts15:29\">28–29</a>).</p><p>Paulo alisisitiza kwamba haijalishi kama mwanaume ametahiriwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:19\">1 Wakorintho 7:19</a>). Kinachojali ni imani inayoonyeshwa kupitia upendo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:6\">Wagalatia 5:6</a>). Katika Wagalatia, Paulo alipinga wapinzani wa Kiyahudi wenye nguvu na akasema kwamba kila mtu anaunganishwa na familia ya Mungu kupitia imani kwa Yesu Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:14-Gal2:21\">Wagalatia 2:14–21</a>). Tohara si muhimu kwa Mungu kumkubali mtu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:6\">Wagalatia 5:6</a>). Kifo cha Yesu msalabani ndicho njia ambayo inawafanya wenye dhambi kuingia katika agano na Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:14-Gal2:21\">Wagalatia 2:14–21</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:9-Gen17:14\">Mwanzo 17:9–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:3\">Mambo ya Walawi 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:2-Josh5:9\">Yoshua 5:2–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:25-Jer9:26\">Yeremia 9:25–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:59\">Luka 1:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:21\">Luka 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:22-John7:24\">Yohana 7:22–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:8\">Matendo 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:1-Acts15:5\">Matendo 15:1–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:19-Acts15:21\">19–21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28-Acts15:31\">28–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:2-Acts16:3\">Matendo 16:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:18-Acts21:24\">Matendo 21:18–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:25-Rom2:29\">Warumi 2:25–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:17-1Cor7:19\">1 Wakorintho 7:17–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:3-Gal2:5\">Wagalatia 2:3–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11-Gal2:21\">11–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:6\">Wagalatia 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:15\">Wagalatia 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:5-Phil3:9\">Wafilipi 3:5–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:11-Col2:23\">Wakolosai 2:11–23</a></p>",
